  "detailed_description": "A pixel Open World Craft Survival RPG.<br>Its characteristics are challenging fights, cooking, and free character development. And its a crude and slow-paced game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adventure and Combat</strong></h2>Hundreds of animals, plants, or monsters, with their own characteristics and combat patterns. Fight them to obtain resources or learn skills. Four combat styles with customizable skills.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/6334c213acf57e2ae372b59afb9faf13.webp?t=1729913193\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><strong>PoleArm</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/de6deb4175a16ae1c6b378a3d64c4870.poster.avif?t=1729913193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/de6deb4175a16ae1c6b378a3d64c4870.webm?t=1729913193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/de6deb4175a16ae1c6b378a3d64c4870.mp4?t=1729913193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Sword/Shield</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/51578bd05235ba77513e4526a9820efe.poster.avif?t=1729913193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/51578bd05235ba77513e4526a9820efe.webm?t=1729913193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/51578bd05235ba77513e4526a9820efe.mp4?t=1729913193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>TwoHand</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/a9c6a60482eb6afa51cca0c215a195b9.poster.avif?t=1729913193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/a9c6a60482eb6afa51cca0c215a195b9.webm?t=1729913193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/a9c6a60482eb6afa51cca0c215a195b9.mp4?t=1729913193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Close Combat</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/a2b7c0c0f2cf152c4c7657f9637b35a5.poster.avif?t=1729913193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/a2b7c0c0f2cf152c4c7657f9637b35a5.webm?t=1729913193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/a2b7c0c0f2cf152c4c7657f9637b35a5.mp4?t=1729913193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Building and Crafting</strong></h2>Build bases, craft equipments, items and magic charms. Over one thousand items, most of which can be crafted.Collect resources, unlock recipes, and plan the cooking/eating reasonably to increase attributes. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/0bf35d2f73c0897fe82fcdb690c1152a.poster.avif?t=1729913193\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410470/extras/0bf35d2f73c0897fe82fcdb690c1152a.webm?t=1729913193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source sr